::Prowl::

Prowl walks up to Iron Raptor, sliding an arm around her waist and 
kissing her cheek. He knew she would be able to feel his love through 
their link, and he liked that fact. The idea that they could both be 
sure that they loved each other always was very interesting.

-Are you allright from the battle, love?- he asks through thought, 
waiting for them to enter the CF.

and she
